:: Start
=== TOTALLY NORMAL TUESDAY ===

You're walking to school when a GIANT METEOR crashes in front of you.

Do you:

[[Stand there and take a selfie with it|Selfie_Meteor]]
[[Jump over it like a cool action hero|Jump_Meteor]]


:: Selfie_Meteor
You pull out your phone for the perfect shot...

The meteor, offended by your flash, rolls over and flattens you.

Your last photo auto-uploads with 47,000 likes.

YOU DIED. (Posthumous influencer, congrats.)

[[*GAME OVER*|Start]]


:: Jump_Meteor
You leap over the meteor doing a perfect triple backflip.

A passing pigeon witnesses it and starts slow-clapping.

You land safely on the other side.

Now a PACK OF ANGRY GEESE blocks the sidewalk, honking like maniacs.

Do you:

[[Try to reason with them calmly|Reason_Geese]]
[[Run straight through them screaming|Runthrough_Geese]]


:: Runthrough_Geese
You sprint into the flock screaming at full volume.

The geese, deeply insulted, form a tornado around you.

You are launched 40 feet into the air and land in a fountain.

A goldfish witnesses everything. He tells no one.

YOU DIED. (Cause of death: disrespecting geese.)

[[*GAME OVER*|Start]]


:: Reason_Geese
You sit down cross-legged and say "I hear you, friends."

The lead goose stares at you for 10 seconds... then bows.

They form a guard of honor and escort you past.

You arrive at school but a ROGUE VENDING MACHINE is blocking the door,
shaking aggressively and demanding exact change.

Do you:

[[Kick it and tell it to calm down|Kick_Machine]]
[[Give it exact change|Pay_Machine]]


:: Kick_Machine
You kick the machine right in the coin slot.

It lets out a mechanical SHRIEK, tips forward,
and pins you to the ground with the full force of 200 bags of Doritos.

Doritos: 1. You: 0.

YOU DIED. (Nacho average ending.)

[[*GAME OVER*|Start]]


:: Pay_Machine
You calmly insert $1.75 in exact nickels.

The machine sighs in relief, hands you a free bag of chips,
and rolls itself politely out of the way.

Inside school, your MATH TEACHER has transformed into a DRAGON
and is demanding everyone solve a quadratic equation or be roasted.

Do you:

[[Actually solve the equation|Solve_Equation]]
[[Compliment the dragon's scales to distract it|Compliment_Dragon]]


:: Compliment_Dragon
The dragon pauses, flustered. "Are... are they periwinkle?"

It gets emotional, cries a single lava tear, and accidentally
sneezes you out the window at 200 mph.

You land on a trampoline, bounce once, and disappear into the clouds.

YOU DIED. (Technically still ascending.)

[[*GAME OVER*|Start]]


:: Solve_Equation
You walk to the board and write out the full solution flawlessly.

The dragon sheds a single tear of pride.

"Finally," it whispers. It transforms back into Mr. Henderson.

He gives you a gold star and an A+ for the semester.

At lunch, an ALIEN SPACESHIP lands in the cafeteria.

The alien points at you specifically and says "YOU. COME."

Do you:

[[Just bolt and hide in your locker|Hide_Locker]]
[[Ask if they have good snacks on the ship first|Ask_Snacks]]


:: Hide_Locker
You sprint to your locker and squeeze inside.

The alien finds you in 4 seconds because you forgot it has 360-degree vision.

It picks up the entire locker, waves goodbye to the cafeteria,
and launches it like a football into deep space.

YOU DIED. (Your locker smells terrible in space too.)

[[*GAME OVER*|Start]]


:: Ask_Snacks
The alien blinks all six of its eyes. "We have... Pringles."

You are immediately teleported aboard.

Turns out the whole universe has been waiting to meet you.

They crown you Galactic Snack Ambassador.

You never have to do homework again.

~~~ YOU WIN! CONGRATULATIONS! ~~~

[[Play Again|Start]]
